{"word":"G1899 - ἔπειτα - épeita - ep'-i-tah - After that","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἔπειτα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">épeita</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep'-i-tah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">After that</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அப்பொழுது, பின்பு - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"thereupon, thereafter, then, afterward"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> nad <a href=\"#/G1534 - εἶτα - eîta - i'-tah/1534\">G1534</a>; <i>thereafter:</i> - after that (-ward), then.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}